{"tid":1366873,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[血汗義士入]義勇軍727要保護示威者","createTime":"2019-07-26T05:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:50:52.000Z","uid":288688,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73c192e65efe6c1a75a501289d7920e0763519be","tid":1366873,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"簡單講哂：<br />\n<br />\n做好準備流血受傷都要保護其他人走先的人：<br />\n－聽日係起點拎紅布，綁係左手臂<br />\n－示威者散水時，守住西鐵站各大出入口<br />\n<br />\n有心運物資、為救護員指路、保護記者，願意幫手疏導人流的人：<br />\n－黃布<br />\n（黃布受傷率會被紅黑布低）<br />\n<br />\n至於黑布：<br />\n－有決心做遊擊隊勇進敵陣的人<br />\n（受傷機率最高）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跪地跪求 屌死氣喉 有志之士 投身勇武革命行列<br />\n<br />\n－「時代革命．暴政必亡」－<br />\n義勇軍出PO組<br />\n求其的司機 上<br />\n2019年7月26日"},{"pid":"e76604ce1495531e3b20d968c98ae039828dfdb9","tid":1366873,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:46:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ccb46cf4ecfeb7f67bdc60b2488091d1186e072","tid":1366873,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bab769d368f7f8c4c7ebc344ad2770d31f5769","tid":1366873,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"負皮嘅唔介意解釋下點解你被負皮? 等我睇下有啲咩可以改善嘅地方"}]}